    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I'm not convinced that showing only the next item adds enough value to justify the extra visual noise, and i'm quite certain that showing the order for all items would be too much.\r\n\r\nInstead, how about we add a \"Next in queue\" / \"Nth in queue\" line to the tooltip of queued items?"
