    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@pchote I'm also concerned about the visual noise. I think that a tooltip would not bring that much value because this is information that has to be available at a glance -- without requiring input from the user. Or as RobotCaleb put it -- it should be passive. \r\n\r\nThe tooltip idea is also not bad as an addition, I may look into that too.\r\n\r\nHow about a small glyph next to the quantity or in the upper right corner? Could be an icon of sorts."
