    "created_at": "2018-11-20T21:05:58Z",
    "updated_at": "2018-11-20T21:05:58Z",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The use case is -- \"I have queued a number of things but I did that some time ago and I can't remember what is next in queue. And the next in queue is pretty important for structures and slow-building items (war factory). It quickly gives me a visual cue of what is coming out next which helps me plan and ensures me that I didn't (or did) mess up the build order.\"\r\n\r\nIt also ties nicely with new priority queueing feature as it gives feedback that my action was successful."
  },
